title: Що Коїться!
overview: How the modern youth of Ivano-Frankivsk lives. "Що Коїться!" series is stories of five completely different residents of Ivano-Frankivsk. Against the background of local streets, the characters talk about their everyday life. The youth drama was created by a group of enthusiasts. The organizers say that the plot of the series is completely fictional and does not concern the real life of the actors.
